high_descs: Turn around and go around the counter to the front of the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn around to go the counter on the other side.
Cut the apple on the counter into three parts.
Place the knife on the top of the golden ladle.
Pick up one piece of the apple.
Turn around and go to the microwave on the left.
Remove the apple piece after heating it in the microwave.
Turn right to the sink.
Place the apple piece into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, step forward, then turn left and walk to the kitchen count, make a right and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle behind the butter knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the bread on the counter.
Slice the apple above the gold colored item.
Put the handle of the knife into the gold colored object.
Pick up the slice of apple closest to the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave which is on the left.
Open the microwave, place the apple inside, close the door and turn on for a few seconds. When finished, remove the apple.
Turn right to face the kitchen sink.
Place the apple in the sink to the right of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a slice of apple in the microwave and place in the sink.

high_descs: turn and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the sharp knife that's in front of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the counter straight ahead.
Slice the apple that's behind the ladle on the counter.
Put the knife down on the counter next to the ladle.
Pick up a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn and walk to the microwave to the right of the stove.
Put the piece of apple inside the microwave, close the door, heat the piece of apple, open the door, take the piece of apple out, and close the door.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the piece of apple inside the sink to the left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of an apple and put it in the sink.
